Class SimObjectList

java.lang.Object
  SimObjectList

public class SimObjectList
extends Object

A List implementation that maintains a list of SimObjects.

Modified by Chris Hoder for Project 9

Made the SimObjectList extend the SimObject so that it has an updateState and a draw method. Draw method is left blank. This List was also converted from a single linked list to a double linked list.
